  "merger_description": "Coles Group Limited (**Coles**) is an Australian public company (ASX: COL) that primarily operates:\n\n* supermarkets nationwide through its subsidiary, Coles Supermarkets Australia Pty Ltd; and\n* retail liquor stores nationwide, trading under the Liquorland, Liquorland Warehouse and Liquorland Cellars brands.\n\nBuiltcom Properties 11 Pty Ltd (**Lessor**) is an Australian private property development and building company, based in Burwood, NSW.\n\nColes Supermarkets Australia Pty Ltd\u00a0has signed a letter of offer in respect of a proposed lease of a Coles supermarket to be constructed within a new mixed-use development at 5 Olympic Drive & 14- 24 Childs Street, Lidcombe NSW (the\u00a0**Acquisition**).\n\nThe proposed Coles supermarket is anticipated to open in January 2030.",
